## The Dataset
The dataset given here contains the data about the sales of the product. 
In the sales and marketing department of this company, there are three types of advertising costs.

### The Goal
Using this dataset, we are looking to predict the future sales according to the advertising expenses.

### The Features
TV:  Advertising cost spent in dollars for advertising on TV;
Radio: Advertising cost spent in dollars for advertising on Radio;
Newspaper: Advertising cost spent in dollars for advertising on Newspaper;
Sales: The amount of product sales in dollars;

